IoT based Smart Irrigation System for Farm

The smart solution for the Irrigation System in farm

As we have Automization in many sectors of our life in not only industries but our houses are also automated. The advancement in IoT technology makes everything automated. We have automation in many household appliances such as Air Conditioner, Heater, Microwave oven etc. So we decided to have an Automation system in our Farms, Gardens, Orchards, Nursery.

The automation in farm can be implemented as automatically watering the plants and crops according to the moisture level or water level in soil of farm.


The aim of this project is to Automate farm using Microcontroller. This project can help farmers to water their crops and plants in farm from remote area. We can also save time using smarter technique we can also save wastage of water. Farmer can have control over watering activities of farm from remote area.
